text:
FWIW, I got:
```julia&gt; @btime vcat(($A[:,:,i] for i = 1:6)...) ;
  16.047 μs (18 allocations: 97.19 KiB)

julia&gt; @btime reduce(vcat, view($A, :, :, i) for i in 1:6) ;
  27.232 μs (22 allocations: 161.25 KiB)

julia&gt; @btime reshape(permutedims($A, (2,3,1)), (128*6,8)) ;
  4.533 μs (3 allocations: 48.14 KiB)```
where I made `A` with
```julia&gt; A = Array(reshape(1:128*8*6, 128,8,6))```

