text:
And with a bigger `A` (with `size(A,3) == 100` instead of `6`):
```julia&gt; @btime reduce(vcat, view($A, :, :, i) for i in 1:100) ;
  5.325 ms (492 allocations: 39.47 MiB)

julia&gt; @btime vcat(($A[:,:,i] for i = 1:100)...) ;
  270.569 μs (210 allocations: 1.58 MiB)

julia&gt; @btime reshape(permutedims($A, (2,3,1)), (128*100,8)) ;
  174.613 μs (3 allocations: 800.14 KiB) ```

